#.  == Translators
#. type: Title =
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Add, remove, merge and transform entries"
msgstr "Añadir, eliminar, fusionar y transformar registros"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:5
msgid "All the instructions below will be for working in the GRSciColl part of the https://registry.gbif.org/[GBIF Registry^]. If you don’t have a login or permissions to add, delete, merge and transform entries, you can do so by using the suggestion system."
msgstr "Todas las instrucciones a continuación serán para trabajar en la parte GRSciColl del https://registry.gbif.org/[GBIF Registry^]. Si no tienes un login o permisos para añadir, borrar, fusionar y transformar entradas, puedes hacerlo usando el sistema de sugerencias."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create entries"
msgstr "Crear registros"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:9
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:18
msgid "To create a new institution go to the https://registry.gbif.org/institution/search[GRSciColl institution tab^], to create a new collection, go to the https://registry.gbif.org/collection/search[GRSciColl collection tab^]."
msgstr "Para crear una nueva institución, vaya a https://registry.gbif.org/institution/search[pestaña institución GRSciColl^], para crear una nueva colección, vaya a https://registry.gbif.org/collection/search[pestaña colección GRSciColl^]."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:10
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:19
msgid "Click on the “create new” button in the upper right corner."
msgstr "Haga clic en el botón Crear nuevo en la esquina superior derecha."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:11
msgid "Fill out the information: only names and codes are mandatory but we strongly recommend to fill in at least one address and country."
msgstr "Rellene la información: solo los nombres y los códigos son obligatorios, pero le recomendamos encarecidamente que rellene al menos una dirección y un país."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:12
msgid "Click on the create button."
msgstr "Haz clic en el botón Crear."

#. type: Title ===
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create entries directly from GBIF dataset or publisher"
msgstr "Crear registros directamente desde el conjunto de datos o el editor de GBIF"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:16
msgid "If you are a GRSciColl editor with the *relevant permissions*, you can create new entries from GBIF datasets or publishers."
msgstr "Si es un editor de GRSciColl con los *permisos pertinentes*, puede crear nuevos registros a partir de conjuntos de datos o editores de GBIF."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:20
msgid "Click on the “create from source” button in the upper right corner."
msgstr "Haga clic en el botón Crear nuevo en la esquina superior derecha."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:21
msgid "Look for the GBIF dataset (if you are creating a collection) or the publisher (if you are creating an institution) that you would like to use."
msgstr "Busque el conjunto de datos de GBIF (si está creando una colección) o el editor (si está creando una institución) que desea utilizar."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:22
msgid "Provide a collection or institution code."
msgstr "Indique un código de colección o de institución."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:23
msgid "Click on “create”."
msgstr "Haz clic en \"crear\"."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:26
msgid "The entries will be created and linked to their sources. Note that the newly created collection entries aren’t associated with any institution by default. You will have to go back to the collection entry and add the institution."
msgstr "Los registros se crearán y se vincularán a sus fuentes. Ten en cuenta que las nuevas colecciones creadas no estarán asociadas a ninguna institución de forma predeterminada. Deberás volver al registro de la colección para agregar la institución."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:27
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/edit-entries.adoc:87
#, no-wrap
msgid "Optional video"
msgstr "Vídeo opcional"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:32
msgid "In this video (02:46), GBIF Data Administrator, Marie Grosjean, describes how to create new entries in GRSciColl."
msgstr "En este vídeo (02:46), la Administradora de Datos de GBIF, Marie Grosjean, describe cómo crear nuevas entradas en GRSciColl."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "Delete entries"
msgstr "Eliminar registros"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:40
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:60
msgid "Click on the entry that you would like to delete."
msgstr "Haga clic en el registro que desea eliminar."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:41
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:61
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:82
msgid "Click on the “More” button in the upper right corner."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:42
msgid "Click on “Deleted this institution” or “Delete this collection”."
msgstr "Haga clic en \"Eliminar esta institución\" o \"Eliminar esta colección\"."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:43
msgid "Confirm the deletion by clicking “yes”."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:46
msgid "Deleted entries can be restored if needed. If you find duplicate entries, we recommend merging them rather than deleting them to avoid the loss of codes and identifiers."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "Merging entries"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:50
msgid "Merging entries means that one of the entries will be deleted and its associated information will be moved to the remaining entry. In addition to that, GRSciColl will display a warning message and show a link to the remaining entry."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:54
msgid "If two entries both have an external source, they cannot be merged."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:55
msgid "Two collections can only be merged if they belong to the same institution."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:58
msgid "In the interface:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:62
msgid "Click on “Merge with other institution” or “Merge with other collection”."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:63
msgid "Select the institution or collection that you would like to keep."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:64
msgid "Click on “Merge”."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:65
msgid "After merging two entries, please review the remaining entry to check if any incorrect data was automatically added during the merge."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:67
msgid "The following will be moved to the remaining entry:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:69
msgid "Any associated identifiers"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:70
msgid "Any associated contacts"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:71
msgid "Any associated collections"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:72
msgid "The codes of the deleted entry will be added as alternative codes to the remaining entry"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:73
msgid "The content of the fields will be moved to the remaining entry if the same field didn’t contain any data originally."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Transform institutions into collection"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:77
msgid "Some institution entries might in fact correspond to collection. On GRSciColl there is a way to transform an institution entry into a collection entry. In practice, the institution entry will be deleted and a new collection entry will be created by reusing the same information. Any collection associated with the original institution will be added under the new institution in addition to the newly created collection."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:79
msgid "Here is how to proceed:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:81
msgid "Click on the institution that you would like to transform."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:83
msgid "Click on “Convert to collection”."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:84
msgid "Choose whether the collection should be under an existing institution or a new one:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:85
msgid "If you would like to create a new institution, check the box “Create under new institution” and enter a name for your new institution. The system will automatically create an institution entry based on the current entry."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:86
msgid "If you would like to associate the collection with an existing institution, use the search box and select the parent institution."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/grscicoll/modules/ROOT/pages/add-remove-entries.adoc:87
msgid "Click the “convert” button."
msgstr ""

